{"tid":2408610,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"長假最後一天多間檢測中心現人龍，有市民稱沒陰性結果明天不能上班，形容「排幾耐都要排」","createTime":"2021-02-15T06:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T07:23:48.000Z","uid":350584,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"42303fe9cad86c4d47e1f0244482017233a09bbb","tid":2408610,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T06:02:09.000Z","msg":"有從事飲食業的市民事前不知道可以預約檢測，又指公司要求她出示病毒檢測證明，否則明天不能上班，形容「排幾耐都要排」。有同樣做飲食的市民事前成功預約檢測名額，又說花了大約45分鐘完成檢測程序，認為整個流程順暢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575746-20210215.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575746-20210215.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4efrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=060bae2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575746-20210215.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=81224f04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575746-20210215.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"b6dba7fdef614ddd4e2ec5300313ca1ba41d0807","tid":2408610,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T06:03:58.000Z","msg":"全港19間社區檢測中心今明兩日預約名額已爆滿，部分檢測中心最快到星期五、初八才有預約名額。多間社區檢測中心出現人龍。梁顯利油麻地社區中心的檢測中心中午時份，無論有預先登記抑或沒有登記人士，都要在排隊等候，閘外大約有數十人，於閘內亦有另外數十人輪候。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35b2ab0ec1d7f1b2c86189efad4126660d84d46","tid":2408610,"uid":268516,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T06:04:23.000Z","msg":"如果檢測中心有人驗到陽性<br />\n咁當日一齊排隊嗰啲會唔會全部要隔離？"},{"pid":"34f932fc18ccc8c81b743576ca361ff18b1126e3","tid":2408610,"uid":102078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T06:06:46.000Z","msg":"臭閪政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c001a5ce988705626d431eb298d95ce2e4af4b8","tid":2408610,"uid":350584,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T06:06:49.000Z","msg":"黎生：我的訴求就是要返工。我今日一定要做完檢測、明天準時返工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a781f8e6026d1f67ec745304af8c7a73bd50b1bd","tid":2408610,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T06:09:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">我要開工群組</span></span></strong> is ready"},{"pid":"dd883bf6ec3f8de82772a1fb725e3e3a11606082","tid":2408610,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a781f8e6026d1f67ec745304af8c7a73bd50b1bd","tid":2408610,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T06:09:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">我要開工群組</span></span></strong> is ready"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T06:21:16.000Z","msg":"檢測群組ready<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba25b71dc167112432427a9522075c754c222122","tid":2408610,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e35b2ab0ec1d7f1b2c86189efad4126660d84d46","tid":2408610,"uid":268516,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T06:04:23.000Z","msg":"如果檢測中心有人驗到陽性<br />\n咁當日一齊排隊嗰啲會唔會全部要隔離？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T06:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"